Super class reference can hold subclass objects

If a superclass reference holds a subclass object and if
    it is calling a overriden function 

     will it copy superclass copy or subclass copy? Subclass copy

If a superclass reference holds a subclass object and if
    it is calling a function that is present only
    in the super class but not in sub class

    can it be called? Yes

If a superclass reference holds a subclass object and if
    it is calling a function that is present only
    in the subclass but not in the superclass

    can it be called ? No
     